September 12th, 2018 X-Wing Vassal news

The X-Wing Vassal League home website is now officially live at this address: http://xwvassal.info

The 2nd edition is now fully playable in this module of X-Wing!
The 1st edition is still playable, but to save space, the art assets were stripped out. To get them back, click on 'Content Checker' and select download all.

Known issues: 
--Recorded games (logfiles) will stack on the autorange firing options lines throughout the match without ever removing them
